      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lyon_Mountain%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "text": "The hamlet once hosted a Lyon Mountain Railroad Station that ferried iron ore to markets across the state.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        3
      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lyon_Mountain%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "text": "The former Lyon Mountain Correctional Facility, a minimum‑security prison, closed in 2011 and was later purchased for sand mining.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        11,
