      ],
      "sourceLabels": [
        "Wikipedia"
      ],
      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Lyon_Mountain%2C_New_York"
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "text": "The 3,840‑foot summit of Lyon Mountain lies just south of the hamlet, overlooking the Saranac River valley.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
        10
